66
00:03:20,934 --> 00:03:22,970
I need your genius.

67
00:03:23,036 --> 00:03:25,573
He likes you.

68
00:03:25,639 --> 00:03:26,740
(LAUGHS)

69
00:03:33,180 --> 00:03:35,416
MEGAN: Butene... Aromatic?

70
00:03:40,020 --> 00:03:41,322
