Aromatics are tough.

73
00:03:46,294 --> 00:03:47,595
Yeah. (LAUGHS)

74
00:03:48,095 --> 00:03:49,363
Um...

75
00:03:49,430 --> 00:03:52,733
I can never figure out
which electrons to put where.

76
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:56,203
You wanna know a trick?
Don't memorize, diagram.

77
00:03:56,270 --> 00:03:58,406
I'm Philip,
by the way. Markoff.

78
00:03:58,472 --> 00:04:00,774
We actually met the
other day for a second.

79
00:04:00,841 --> 00:04:03,311
