93
00:04:38,912 --> 00:04:42,115
I think you should be
cutting loose, airing
out your brain.

94
00:04:42,182 --> 00:04:43,717
Right. Right.

95
00:04:43,784 --> 00:04:46,554
So, when I fail
the test tomorrow,
can I write that theory in

96
00:04:46,620 --> 00:04:49,757
