103
00:05:06,707 --> 00:05:10,711
You don't even know me.
Oh, my God. That's true.

104
00:05:10,778 --> 00:05:13,013
Wow. Okay. Then come on.
I'll quiz you on the way.

105
00:05:13,080 --> 00:05:14,615
