before an exam.

107
00:05:17,017 --> 00:05:19,353
You know what?
I really have to study,

108
00:05:19,420 --> 00:05:21,655
and I'm not that, you know,

109
00:05:21,722 --> 00:05:24,592
"run away with a guy I've
