type of girl, so...

110
00:05:24,658 --> 00:05:28,996
Okay. (CLEARS THROAT)
Um... Okay.

111
00:05:29,062 --> 00:05:34,001
SUNY, Albany, summa cum laude.
B.U. med school, second year,

112
00:05:34,067 --> 00:05:36,169
