Not bragging.

113
00:05:36,236 --> 00:05:38,205
I love animals.
I don't like birds, though.

114
00:05:38,271 --> 00:05:40,508
I am an unapologetic member
of the Young Republicans,

115
00:05:40,574 --> 00:05:43,210
