like to talk politics.

116
00:05:43,276 --> 00:05:44,845
Sometimes I work too hard.

117
00:05:44,912 --> 00:05:48,248
And when I was little,
I really hated wearing
full-length pants.

118
00:05:48,315 --> 00:05:50,618
