124
00:06:08,569 --> 00:06:11,572
Right. Clothes.
All right. I'll pick
you up at 7:30, then.

125
00:06:14,608 --> 00:06:16,276
Okay.
All right.

126
00:06:29,890 --> 00:06:31,825
Okay.
So the trick
to roulette,

127
00:06:31,892 --> 00:06:34,995
or at least my theory is
you gotta feel the numbers.

128
00:06:35,062 --> 00:06:38,331
You know, you gotta really,
really kind of get in
sync with the wheel.

129
00:06:38,398 --> 00:06:39,767
