Yes, of course
it was your fault.

141
00:07:02,222 --> 00:07:04,458
Fine. Blame it on me. (LAUGHS)
You're a bad person.

142
00:07:04,525 --> 00:07:05,726
WAITRESS: Your drinks, sir.

143
00:07:05,793 --> 00:07:07,227
Thank you.

144
00:07:07,294 --> 00:07:09,096
