It's a school night.

146
00:07:11,431 --> 00:07:13,667
All right.
Trust me, though.

147
00:07:13,734 --> 00:07:17,137
The rush is gonna
be good for you,
it releases the endorphins,

148
00:07:17,204 --> 00:07:21,008
