Cyclopropene.

149
00:07:21,975 --> 00:07:24,077
Uh... Aromatic?

150
00:07:24,144 --> 00:07:26,013
There you go.
(LAUGHING)

151
00:07:26,079 --> 00:07:28,849
See? You know this stuff.
You just got to
trust yourself. Okay.

152
00:07:28,916 --> 00:07:30,884
Oh, okay.
Take these.

153
00:07:30,951 --> 00:07:32,853
Close your eyes.
MEGAN: Okay.

154
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:34,955
