MEGAN: Yes.

158
00:07:41,895 --> 00:07:44,498
Oh, my God!
DEALER: We got a winner here.

159
00:07:45,833 --> 00:07:48,368
That's insane. Look at that.

160
00:07:49,236 --> 00:07:51,739
Oh, my God.
Wow.

161
00:07:51,805 --> 00:07:53,774
(LAUGHING)

162
