I'm gonna tell them.

191
00:09:34,775 --> 00:09:36,176
Okay.

192
00:09:36,243 --> 00:09:39,012
Hey, I have an idea.
Uh-oh.

193
00:09:39,079 --> 00:09:40,614
How about we
stop unpacking...

194
00:09:40,681 --> 00:09:43,516
Mmm-hmm.
...order Chinese food
and study together?

195
00:09:43,583 --> 00:09:45,485
Well, that sounds nice.

196
00:09:45,552 --> 00:09:48,488
