(SIGHS)

205
00:10:10,543 --> 00:10:11,979
What, are those
applications?

206
00:10:12,045 --> 00:10:14,682
Yep. I only have
one more to go.

207
00:10:14,748 --> 00:10:17,117
All right, all right.
Well, you're getting
into B.U.,

208
00:10:17,184 --> 00:10:18,585
so I wouldn't stress it.

209
00:10:20,053 --> 00:10:22,222
I like you.
I like you, too.

210
00:10:23,590 --> 00:10:25,458
Do you really have to go?
Yeah, I do.

211
00:10:25,525 --> 00:10:27,327
But I will kiss you
right when I get home.

212
00:10:27,394 --> 00:10:28,996
Okay?
Okay.

213
00:10:30,063 --> 00:10:31,098
I love you.

214
00:10:31,164 --> 00:10:32,833
I love you, too.

215
00:10:32,900 --> 00:10:34,134
Bye.

216
00:10:34,201 --> 00:10:35,836
Bye.

217
00:10:40,774 --> 00:10:42,542
MEGAN: I feel like a tourist.

218
00:10:42,609 --> 00:10:45,512
PHILIP: Just, you know,
squint your eyes, and then
pretend you're in Paris.

219
00:10:46,213 --> 00:10:47,748
