Is that better?

224
00:10:56,957 --> 00:10:58,191
Mmm... Much better.
Thank you.

225
00:10:58,258 --> 00:10:59,793
You're welcome.
I'm gonna start
calling you Pocket.

226
00:10:59,860 --> 00:11:01,729
How about that?
