more than to marry you, but...

234
00:11:26,686 --> 00:11:28,288
But what?

235
00:11:29,689 --> 00:11:31,959
I haven't even graduated yet,

236
00:11:32,025 --> 00:11:34,661
and you're still
in med school and you
haven't even met my parents.

237
00:11:34,728 --> 00:11:37,230
Well, let's go.
Right now. Tonight.

238
00:11:37,297 --> 00:11:39,199
We can leave this second.
